<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Search_Lucene query parser throws an exception if query doesn't conform to query language.</p>

<p>It's necessary to have an option to parse any user input without exceptions.</p>

    </div>
</div>

